title: Weihao Cui
text:
Weihao Cui
Currently, I am a postdoc research fellow working with Prof. Bingsheng He and Prof. Minyi Guo. I am jointly supported by the National University of Singapore and Shanghai Jiao Tong University. I work closely with Prof. Quan Chen and Dr. Han Zhao.
I obtained my Ph.D. degree at Department of Computer Science and Engineering (CSE), Shanghai Jiao Tong University, China, supervised by Prof. Quan Chen on AI System and Cloud Computing.


Research Interest

System for Machine Learning
Resource Management of GPU
High Performance Computing



Education

Sept 2017 - Mar 2020 Ph.D. in Computer Science and Technology Advisor: Prof. Quan Chen Shanghai Jiao Tong University, China
Sept 2020 - Sept 2023 Master in Computer Science and Technology Advisor: Prof. Quan Chen Shanghai Jiao Tong University, China



Affiliation

Xtra Computing Group National University of Singapore Singapore
Emerging Parallel Computing Center Shanghai Jiao Tong University Shanghai, China
